<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Line Coding Simulator — Sistem Telekomunikasi</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --bg:#080b12;--surface:#0f1320;--surface2:#161b2e;--surface3:#1e2540;
  --border:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.13);--border2:rgba(90,110,210,0.28);
  --accent:#4f6fff;--accent2:#7b9fff;--glow:rgba(79,111,255,0.18);
  --text:#e8ecf4;--text2:#8b95b0;--text3:#a0b4ff;
  --mono:'Space Mono',monospace;--sans:'DM Sans',sans-serif;
  --c1:#4f6fff;--c2:#00c9a7;--c3:#ff6b6b;--c4:#ffd166;--c5:#c77dff;--c6:#ff9f1c;--c7:#e76f51;--c8:#06d6a0;
}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(79,111,255,0.025) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(79,111,255,0.025) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:44px 44px;pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
.wrap{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 22px;position:relative;z-index:1}

/* HEADER */
header{padding:44px 0 28px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:40px}
.htag{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.htag::before{content:'';width:22px;height:1px;background:var(--accent)}
h1{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:clamp(22px,4vw,40px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-.02em}
h1 em{color:var(--accent2);font-style:normal}
.sub{color:var(--text2);font-size:14px;font-weight:300;margin-top:6px}

/* TABS */
.tabs{display:flex;gap:3px;margin-bottom:28px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:5px;overflow-x:auto}
.tab{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11.5px;padding:9px 18px;border-radius:8px;border:none;background:transparent;color:var(--text2);cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;white-space:nowrap;letter-spacing:.04em}
.tab:hover{color:var(--text);background:var(--surface2)}
.tab.on{background:var(--accent);color:#fff}
.sec{display:none}.sec.on{display:block;animation:fadeUp .3s ease}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

/* CARD */
.card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:26px;margin-bottom:18px}
.ctitle{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--accent2);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:18px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.ctitle::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border)}

/* INPUTS */
.row2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px;margin-bottom:18px}
@media(max-width:640px){.row2{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
label{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);font-family:var(--mono);letter-spacing:.04em;display:block;margin-bottom:6px}
.binput{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:10px;color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.12em;padding:13px 16px;width:100%;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s}
.binput:focus{border-color:var(--accent)}
select{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:8px;color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;padding:8px 12px;outline:none;cursor:pointer;width:100%}
.hint{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);font-family:var(--mono);margin-top:4px}

/* BIT DISPLAY */
.bits{display:flex;gap:3px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:10px}
.bc{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface2);color:var(--text3);transition:all .2s}
.bc.b1{background:rgba(79,111,255,.15);border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent2)}
.bc.b0{color:var(--text3)}

/* METHOD BTNs */
.mgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(148px,1fr));gap:9px}
.mb{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:11px 14px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface2);color:var(--text2);cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.04em}
.mb:hover{border-color:var(--border2);color:var(--text)}
.mb.on{border-color:transparent}
.mb.on.m1{background:rgba(79,111,255,.18);border-color:var(--c1);color:var(--c1)}
.mb.on.m2{background:rgba(0,201,167,.12);border-color:var(--c2);color:var(--c2)}
.mb.on.m3{background:rgba(255,107,107,.12);border-color:var(--c3);color:var(--c3)}
.mb.on.m4{background:rgba(255,209,102,.12);border-color:var(--c4);color:var(--c4)}
.mb.on.m5{background:rgba(199,125,255,.12);border-color:var(--c5);color:var(--c5)}
.mb.on.m6{background:rgba(255,159,28,.12);border-color:var(--c6);color:var(--c6)}
.mb.on.m7{background:rgba(231,111,81,.12);border-color:var(--c7);color:var(--c7)}
.dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
.d1{background:var(--c1)}.d2{background:var(--c2)}.d3{background:var(--c3)}.d4{background:var(--c4)}.d5{background:var(--c5)}.d6{background:var(--c6)}.d7{background:var(--c7)}

/* WAVEFORM */
.wbox{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:18px;margin-bottom:16px;overflow-x:auto}
.wrow{display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:14px}
.wlabel{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;width:88px;flex-shrink:0;letter-spacing:.04em}
canvas.wc{border-radius:5px}
.empty{text-align:center;padding:44px;color:var(--text3);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.05em;animation:pulse 2s infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.35}}

/* STATS */
.srow{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:14px}
.sc{background:var(--surface3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:7px 12px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text2)}
.sc b{color:var(--text)}

/* TRACE TABLE */
.trace-wrap{overflow-x:auto;margin-top:14px}
table.tr{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px}
table.tr th{background:var(--surface3);padding:7px 11px;text-align:center;color:var(--text3);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;border:1px solid var(--border)}
table.tr td{padding:7px 11px;text-align:center;border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text2)}
table.tr tr:nth-child(even) td{background:var(--surface2)}

/* THEORY CARDS */
.tgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-bottom:18px}
.tc{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:20px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .2s}
.tc:hover{border-color:var(--border2)}
.tc::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:3px;height:100%;border-radius:3px 0 0 3px}
.tc.t1::before{background:var(--c1)}.tc.t2::before{background:var(--c2)}.tc.t3::before{background:var(--c3)}.tc.t4::before{background:var(--c4)}.tc.t5::before{background:var(--c5)}.tc.t6::before{background:var(--c6)}.tc.t7::before{background:var(--c7)}.tc.t8::before{background:var(--c8)}
.tname{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:2px}
.t1 .tname{color:var(--c1)}.t2 .tname{color:var(--c2)}.t3 .tname{color:var(--c3)}.t4 .tname{color:var(--c4)}.t5 .tname{color:var(--c5)}.t6 .tname{color:var(--c6)}.t7 .tname{color:var(--c7)}.t8 .tname{color:var(--c8)}
.tfull{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:10px;font-style:italic}
.tdesc{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:12px}
.rulebox{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:11px 13px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.9}
.rulebox strong{color:var(--text)}
.badges{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:10px}
.badge{font-size:9px;font-family:var(--mono);padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;letter-spacing:.04em}
.bp{background:rgba(0,201,167,.12);color:var(--c2);border:1px solid rgba(0,201,167,.25)}
.bn{background:rgba(255,107,107,.09);color:var(--c3);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,107,.18)}
.bm{background:rgba(79,111,255,.1);color:var(--accent2);border:1px solid rgba(79,111,255,.2)}

/* VIDEO EMBED */
.vid-wrap{margin-top:14px;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--border);background:#000;aspect-ratio:16/9;width:100%}
.vid-wrap video{width:100%;height:100%;display:block;max-height:280px}

/* COMPARISON TABLE */
.ctable{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12.5px}
.ctable th{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);letter-spacing:.07em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:9px 14px;text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.ctable td{padding:11px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(90,110,200,.05);color:var(--text2);vertical-align:middle}
.ctable tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
.ctable tr:hover td{background:var(--surface2)}
.mtag{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px}
.tic{color:var(--c2)}.crs{color:var(--c3)}.mid{color:var(--c4)}

/* QUIZ */
.qcard{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:28px;margin-bottom:18px}
.qprog{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:22px}
.pbar{flex:1;height:3px;background:var(--surface3);border-radius:3px;margin:0 10px;overflow:hidden}
.pfill{height:100%;background:var(--accent);border-radius:3px;transition:width .4s ease}
.pscore{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text2)}
.qq{font-size:15px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.55}
.qsub{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--accent2);background:var(--surface2);display:inline-block;padding:3px 11px;border-radius:6px;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:20px}
.qopts{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:9px;margin-bottom:20px}
@media(max-width:540px){.qopts{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.qopt{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:11px 14px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);letter-spacing:.03em;text-align:left}
.qopt:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--text)}
.qopt.correct{border-color:var(--c2);background:rgba(0,201,167,.1);color:var(--c2)}
.qopt.wrong{border-color:var(--c3);background:rgba(255,107,107,.09);color:var(--c3)}
.qfb{font-size:13px;padding:13px 16px;border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:18px;display:none;line-height:1.65}
.qfb.show{display:block}
.qfb.correct{background:rgba(0,201,167,.09);border:1px solid rgba(0,201,167,.28);color:var(--c2)}
.qfb.wrong{background:rgba(255,107,107,.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,107,.18);color:#ff8c8c}
.btnp{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:10px;padding:11px 26px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;letter-spacing:.05em;transition:all .2s}
.btnp:hover{background:var(--accent2);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.btng{background:transparent;color:var(--accent2);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:10px;padding:9px 20px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;letter-spacing:.05em;transition:all .2s}
.btng:hover{background:var(--surface2)}
.qresult{text-align:center;padding:22px 0;display:none}
.qscore-big{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:52px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:6px}
.qmsg{color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:22px}

.authors{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:14px;padding:12px 16px;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;width:fit-content}
.author-label{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase}
.author-name{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--accent2);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.03em}
.author-nim{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);background:var(--surface3);padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;border:1px solid var(--border)}
.author-sep{color:var(--text3)}
footer{margin-top:70px;padding:28px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--border);text-align:center;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);letter-spacing:.07em}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px;height:5px}
::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--surface)}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--surface3);border-radius:3px}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
<header>
  <div class="htag">Sistem Telekomunikasi &amp; Komunikasi Data</div>
  <h1>Line Coding <em>Simulator</em></h1>
  <p class="sub">Simulasi interaktif · Teori lengkap · Video pembelajaran · Kuis 10 soal</p>
  <div class="authors">
    <span class="author-label">Disusun oleh:</span>
    <span class="author-name">Kankan Kusumawardana</span>
    <span class="author-nim">NIM 24051030076</span>
    <span class="author-sep">·</span>
    <span class="author-name">Ahmad Rizal Ardiyansah</span>
    <span class="author-nim">NIM 24051030088</span>
  </div>
</header>

<nav class="tabs">
  <button class="tab on"  onclick="sw('theory',this)">📚 Teori &amp; Video</button>
  <button class="tab"     onclick="sw('compare',this)">📊 Perbandingan</button>
  <button class="tab"     onclick="sw('sim',this)">⚡ Simulator</button>
  <button class="tab"     onclick="sw('quiz',this)">🧪 Kuis</button>
</nav>

<!-- ============================================================ SIMULATOR -->
<div id="sec-sim" class="sec">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="ctitle">Input Bit Stream</div>
    <div class="row2">
      <div>
        <label>Masukkan deretan bit biner (maks 20 bit)</label>
        <input class="binput" id="bitIn" type="text" placeholder="contoh: 10110010" maxlength="20" autocomplete="off" oninput="onBit()">
        <div class="hint" id="bhint">Ketik kombinasi 0 dan 1</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label>Preset contoh</label>
        <select onchange="loadPre(this.value)">
          <option value="">— pilih preset —</option>
          <option value="10110010">10110010</option>
          <option value="11001100">11001100</option>
          <option value="01010101">01010101</option>
          <option value="11110000">11110000</option>
          <option value="10000001">10000001 (uji B8ZS)</option>
          <option value="000000001">000000001 (uji HDB3)</option>
        </select>
        <div class="hint" style="margin-top:8px">Pilih contoh bit stream</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bits" id="bdis"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="ctitle">Pilih Metode Encoding</div>
    <div class="mgrid">
      <button class="mb m1 on" onclick="tog('nrz-l',this)"><span class="dot d1"></span>NRZ-L</button>
      <button class="mb m2 on" onclick="tog('nrz-i',this)"><span class="dot d2"></span>NRZ-I</button>
      <button class="mb m3 on" onclick="tog('ami',this)"><span class="dot d3"></span>AMI</button>
      <button class="mb m4 on" onclick="tog('manchester',this)"><span class="dot d4"></span>Manchester</button>
      <button class="mb m5"    onclick="tog('diff-man',this)"><span class="dot d5"></span>Diff. Manchester</button>
      <button class="mb m6"    onclick="tog('rz',this)"><span class="dot d6"></span>RZ</button>
      <button class="mb m7"    onclick="tog('b8zs',this)"><span class="dot d7"></span>B8ZS</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="ctitle">Visualisasi Gelombang</div>
    <div id="warea"><div class="empty">↑ Masukkan bit stream untuk melihat gelombang</div></div>
    <div id="sarea" style="display:none"><div class="srow" id="srow"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" id="traceCard" style="display:none">
    <div class="ctitle">Step-by-Step Trace</div>
    <div id="traceBody"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============================================================ THEORY -->
<div id="sec-theory" class="sec on">

  <!-- UNIPOLAR NRZ -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="ctitle">Unipolar</div>
    <div class="tgrid">
      <div class="tc t1">
        <div class="tname">Unipolar NRZ</div>
        <div class="tfull">Non-Return to Zero — Unipolar</div>
        <div class="tdesc">Skema paling sederhana. Hanya menggunakan satu polaritas tegangan. Bit <strong>1</strong> direpresentasikan sebagai tegangan positif (+V), bit <strong>0</strong> sebagai 0 volt. Tidak ada transisi kembali ke nol di tengah periode bit.</div>
        <div class="rulebox"><strong>Aturan:</strong><br>Bit 1 → +V<br>Bit 0 → 0V</div>
        <div class="badges">
          <span class="badge bp">✓ Sederhana</span>
          <span class="badge bn">✗ DC component besar</span>
          <span class="badge bn">✗ Tidak self-clocking</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vid-wrap">
          <video controls style="width:100%;height:100%;display:block;background:#000;border:none" preload="metadata"><source src="videos/unipolar-nrz.mp4" type="video/mp4">Browser Anda tidak mendukung tag video.</video></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tc t8">
        <div class="tname">Unipolar RZ</div>
        <div class="tfull">Return to Zero — Unipolar</div>
        <div class="tdesc">Varian unipolar di mana sinyal <em>kembali ke nol</em> di tengah periode bit jika bit bernilai 1. Bit <strong>0</strong> tetap di 0V sepanjang periode. Transisi kembali ke nol membantu sinkronisasi clock.</div>
        <div class="rulebox"><strong>Aturan:</strong><br>Bit 1 → +V separuh pertama, 0V separuh kedua<br>Bit 0 → 0V sepanjang periode</div>
        <div class="badges">
          <span class="badge bp">✓ Membantu sinkronisasi</span>
          <span class="badge bn">✗ Butuh 2× bandwidth</span>
          <span class="badge bn">✗ Masih ada DC component</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vid-wrap">
          <video controls style="width:100%;height:100%;display:block;background:#000;border:none" preload="metadata"><source src="videos/rz.mp4" type="video/mp4">Browser Anda tidak mendukung tag video.</video></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- POLAR -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="ctitle">Polar — NRZ</div>
    <div class="tgrid">
      <div class="tc t1">
        <div class="tname">NRZ-L</div>
        <div class="tfull">Non-Return to Zero — Level</div>
        <div class="tdesc">Menggunakan dua polaritas tegangan. Level tegangan langsung merepresentasikan nilai bit. Bit <strong>1</strong> → tegangan tinggi (+V), bit <strong>0</strong> → tegangan rendah (−V). Tidak ada transisi di tengah periode.</div>
        <div class="rulebox"><strong>Aturan:</strong><br>Bit 1 → +V<br>Bit 0 → −V</div>
        <div class="badges">
          <span class="badge bp">✓ Efisiensi bandwidth tinggi</span>
          <span class="badge bn">✗ DC component</span>
          <span class="badge bn">✗ Synchronization problem</span>
          <span class="badge bm">≈ Internal data bus</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vid-wrap">
          <video controls style="width:100%;height:100%;display:block;background:#000;border:none" preload="metadata"><source src="videos/nrz-l.mp4" type="video/mp4">Browser Anda tidak mendukung tag video.</video></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tc t2">
        <div class="tname">NRZ-I</div>
        <div class="tfull">Non-Return to Zero — Invert on 1</div>
        <div class="tdesc">Menggunakan <em>transisi</em> bukan level absolut. Transisi terjadi di awal periode bit ketika bit <strong>1</strong>. Bit <strong>0</strong> tidak menghasilkan transisi. Lebih tahan terhadap pembalikan polaritas kabel.</div>
        <div class="rulebox"><strong>Aturan:</strong><br>Bit 1 → Transisi (invert level saat ini)<br>Bit 0 → Tidak ada transisi</div>
        <div class="badges">
          <span class="badge bp">✓ Tahan polar inversion</span>
          <span class="badge bn">✗ String 0 panjang = masalah sync</span>
          <span class="badge bm">≈ USB 2.0</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vid-wrap">
          <video controls style="width:100%;height:100%;display:block;background:#000;border:none" preload="metadata"><source src="videos/nrz-i.mp4" type="video/mp4">Browser Anda tidak mendukung tag video.</video></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
